  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/9cfaf431dfa6469dcbb37bfc40b1f9cb.avif?t=1668442775\" width=598 height=194 /></span><br>PHYAKH is  a story-driven, action adventure combining exploration with fast-paced combat games. You’ll become PHYAKH, a creature who was saved from death in scientific laboratory in bio-robotic body and comeback to help his wife from under arrested by the army troop<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/7529165de8c1c82bbba28613877a2b7e.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/ca03261e3314ae11be6557a652fa269c.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><strong>Key Features</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore brand new fantasy open-world maps </h2>Collect the diamond pearls use as an extra energy source for his bio-robotic suit<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/acd9ec07f097a80611f6b373a548efb6.poster.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/acd9ec07f097a80611f6b373a548efb6.webm?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/acd9ec07f097a80611f6b373a548efb6.mp4?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/27c3abfa8264e37320ed536303bdc02d.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage in Fast-Paced Combat</h2>Choosing the right creatures with unique abilities to take down the Invader, army troops were scattered all over the planet.<br>Kotcha-weha  for Simultaneous Combat Over the cloud<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/3da39c51cb1cc88713f19b9b7dd92cb3.poster.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/3da39c51cb1cc88713f19b9b7dd92cb3.webm?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/3da39c51cb1cc88713f19b9b7dd92cb3.mp4?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Phyakh for Simultaneous Combat On Ground continue to Underwater Fight<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/a4db2b0835c5a349fa7c19dc3ab0068e.poster.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/a4db2b0835c5a349fa7c19dc3ab0068e.webm?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/a4db2b0835c5a349fa7c19dc3ab0068e.mp4?t=1668442775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sriha for Explore over the SuperNatural Environment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/008c7d4e5c9591995cf43afc7043a54a.poster.avif?t=1668442775\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149270/extras/008c7d4e5c9591995cf43afc7043a54a.webm?t=16